      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHADY LADY (6) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 26.10 beating Mighty Heighty. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can make it two on the bounce. STITCH AND SHOUT (7) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (26.39) at this track in a Grade 5. Well placed here and should do much better. DARNUM DUKE (4) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (29.19) in a Grade 5 at Sale. Solid record here winning two races. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Has ability and can atone. EXTINCT (8) is worth including after a top-three finish most recently.",
